{"tid":213491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安]啱啱有陌生人㩒門鐘","createTime":"2017-04-23T07:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T15:51:57.000Z","uid":59165,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd9455b4eb4e94a5164f96188cfc325f28c73d6","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的 頭先係屋企訓緊教 突然聽到有人㩒鐘<br />\n之後我起身著返件褸就望下係邊個先<br />\n<br />\n我一伸個頭去望 就見到有個男人 著黑綠色衫 好似係<br />\n睇唔到樣 因為我打算開佢已經轉身開後樓梯門走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然有種好不安感覺 所以我無開到 <br />\n依加諗返起 如果係速遞之類應該會企多陣或者㩒多幾下 <br />\n而且落去都撘𨋢啦 點會行後樓梯走 我住廿樓<br />\n<br />\n好唔好依加落去問下看更 好驚一走左屋企會比人襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699415fe54ecd517886711b57965b13be5c32bdb","tid":213491,"uid":66254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"香檳大廈?"},{"pid":"c947ce70bdaf27e55e64bb6d14f2a50c79616d6a","tid":213491,"uid":10338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"佢再㩒先算<br />\n因為通常恐怖電影劇情<br />\n你咁會累死個保安"},{"pid":"39a93cbcbf632a95aa83eac24fa9344d081f65c6","tid":213491,"uid":75445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢再㩒先算<br />\n因為通常恐怖電影劇情<br />\n你咁會累死個保安</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8cf37521a1ce4c0b75d61f5f8beeacc506d06f","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香檳大廈?</blockquote><br />\n唔係個隻鐘仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a788d54b4e904f5ef9183b2482f96ec13828c9a","tid":213491,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"抄水錶呀"},{"pid":"dbfeb0f85cae5908316470f5bb92faa5963a6df4","tid":213491,"uid":105002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會係㩒完鐘先發現自己去錯層 就行樓梯去翻啱咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95239a2399bd96d5bc80c2033a6b9515250d1cd0","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢再㩒先算<br />\n因為通常恐怖電影劇情<br />\n你咁會累死個保安</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會累死佢 我想問下佢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見件衫又似制服又似風褸 我都睇唔清 淨係知個刻好不安<br />\n完全唔敢開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268b93605db4136f29e864b02c2fa78485f71aee","tid":213491,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"開門比佢知屋企有人咪唔搞你囉"},{"pid":"c817e5ab6919992d024686236738c3b8c87ac73f","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢會唔會係㩒完鐘先發現自己去錯層 就行樓梯去翻啱咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩有一秒諗會唔會住上面跌左衫落黎先落黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897be1b21a11f7bcded6ab25ca4315b904dca3e","tid":213491,"uid":90631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"拎住把刀目光呆滯，一路傻笑咁開門，實唔會搞你"},{"pid":"b4051ab332a5bb6052dfc4f32dc099102637efc9","tid":213491,"uid":105865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎住把刀目光呆滯，一路傻笑咁開門，實唔會搞你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d541d102bbb5d8756b2b6649a6fcba6845f8cc4a","tid":213491,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"同看更夾埋架啦, 想爆你格"},{"pid":"9936f91f1e41b42c81d