g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 啱先仲同d呀姐談笑風生"},{"pid":"6df4402a1bbe92434ca0e743238501ceeb689ff2","tid":213491,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我落左去問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個看更話無人登記過 唔為意有黑綠色衫既人 幫我留意下之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友d舉動令我好不安 屌佢</blockquote><br />\n嗰個真係看更嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 啱先仲同d呀姐談笑風生</blockquote><br />\n成個局黎架, 你以為佢地真係同你FD <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2423b718125a61a37121dda5001aed14efb816f","tid":213491,"uid":39468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"禁鐘係想知道屋入面有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人開門就冇事 冇人開門就到佢開門"},{"pid":"383fbce06ea353e5fc70d26eb9a837c2556f886c","tid":213491,"uid":41614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8beabadbf79d5a1ad4beefd1d57bb4c5a46e728","tid":213491,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"個情節好熟口面但醒唔起幾時見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打指點下迷津？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed920a6b157a43931af36e7f3a6d197149bd9a77","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禁鐘係想知道屋入面有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人開門就冇事 冇人開門就到佢開門</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到屋企都會有比人爆格既一日<br />\n今日我會守住係屋企<br />\n<br />\n咁我好無問下隔離屋有無比人㩒鐘"},{"pid":"1e3b5be7e703d1943c8ab968e2c4dadf9cc25433","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬唔好死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依加不安完諗落越黎越嬲 聽日仲要返工 比我抖下得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事後心中有團火"},{"pid":"02a93ae5bbfd55e9c290f2ce8522f1073d9a787a","tid":213491,"uid":93436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"係咪踩線呀"},{"pid":"ccbfbe8706900b2a0ceec38d06b323b90ad27e11","tid":213491,"uid":52093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"我記得有次番屋企<br />\n搭左另一部𨋢行一層番去<br />\n我都見到有條友坐係樓梯度<br />\n佢見到我仲跟住望我住邊戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣都怕怕地<br />\n原來佢係要抄錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢禁過鐘發覺我屋企冇人就坐係樓梯口個邊等"},{"pid":"56413958ddba7bb01732f28be84609a9f207631c","tid":213491,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20150227/photo/0227-00407-056b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150227%2Fphoto%2F0227-00407-056b2.jpg&h=df617538&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9975994605f26479b98d33f229f4fcfefe16163b","tid":213491,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得有次番屋企<br />\n搭左另一部𨋢行一層番去<br />\n我都見到有條友坐係樓梯度<br />\n佢見到我仲跟住望我住邊戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣都怕怕地<br />\n原來佢係要抄錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢禁過鐘發覺我屋企冇人就坐係樓梯口個邊等</blockquote><br />\n佢無等我就走左 我已經即刻彈起身著褸跑出去 <br />\n因為驚係屋企人拎好多野無手開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\