lockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有 會驚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n上次有條個陌生人戴口罩係到㩒門鐘<br />\n果時一個人屋企都有少少怯<br />\n後尾原來走廊要唔知做啲咩裝修野<br />\n我都唔記得到底佢果時搵我做乜</blockquote><br />\n我都好驚 得自己一個逼住開門會開好細條隙問咩事<br />\n聽得以前啲咩迷暈煙黨多 驚中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我係眼仔見到唔識既人<br />\n自己一個係屋企直情唔會開門"},{"pid":"4c5d42ae588309341ef1839206530b32edcdb7ee","tid":213491,"uid":46863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"好彩屋企冇門鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8436593cf376891ce029ed14587faea580c14d2","tid":213491,"uid":47568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"哇屌<br />\n樓主小心 呢幾日一定要有人係屋企"}]}